        <p class="text-s-red">WHAT IS NIACINAMIDE?</p>
        <p>Niacinamide, also known as nicotinamide, is a form of Vitamin B3 that is beneficial to hair health and can potentially speed up the rate of hair regrowth seen in combination with minoxidil and a DHT blocker. Niacinamide is also thought to restore damaged hair and increase body and suppleness of hair for the appearance of thicker locks.</p>
        <p class="text-s-red">WHAT OTHER BENEFICIAL INGREDIENTS ARE IN HERE?</p>
        <p>Both our Thickening Shampoo and Conditioner contain niacinamide as well as other ingredients that are popular in hair loss shampoos for their hair growth benefits.</p>
        <p><span class="text-s-red">ROSEMARY OIL </span> - Found in both our Thickening Shampoo and Conditioner, rosemary oil has been commonly used to promote hair groth similar to minoxidil.</p>
        <p><span class="text-s-red">PANTHENOL </span> - Found in our Thickening Shampoo is believed to have benefits for hair thickness and moisture retention.</p>
        <p><span class="text-s-red">ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE </span> - Found in our Thickening Shampoo, aloe may help promote a healthy scalp and help condition and repair damaged hair.</p>
        <p><span class="text-s-red">BIOTIN </span> - Found in our Thickening Conditioner, is a form of Vitamin B. While there is little known about the effects of biotihn on hair growth, a biotin deficiency is known to lead to hair loss, indicating it is important to your hair health.</p>
        <p><span class="text-s-red">CAFFEINE </span> - Found in our Thickening Conditioner, caffeine has been shown to extend the growth phase of hair follicles and works well in combination with minoxidil and or DHT blockers.</p>
